Installation instructions:
-------------------------

$ # Download the library
$ # Unpack
$ cd rtipc
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make
$ make install

This installs rtipc to the default directory /opt/etherlab. For other cmake
options, see CMakeLists.txt
